<view class="wrap"><view class="header"><view class="box"><image class="icon" src="../../static/icon_position.png" mode="aspectFit"></image><view class="info"><view class="class">{{grade}}</view><view class="school">{{school}}</view></view></view></view><view class="content"><scroll-view class="scroll_view" scroll-x="true"><view class="list"><block wx:for="{{list}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><block><image class="cover" src="{{item.img}}" mode="aspectFill" lazy-load="true"></image></block></block></view></scroll-view><view class="paper_box"><image class="bg" src="../../static/page_content.png" mode="widthFix"></image><view class="paper_content"><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">姓名：</text><input type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','name','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.name}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">生日：</text><input type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','birthday','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.birthday}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">QQ：</text><input type="number" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','qq','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.qq}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex"><text class="label">父母电话：</text><input type="number" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','father_phone','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.father_phone}}" bindinput="__e"/><text class="interval">/</text><input type="number" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','mother_phone','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.mother_phone}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">我家的地址：</text><input type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','address','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.address}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">我的爱好：</text><input type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','hobby','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.hobby}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">人生座右铭：</text><input type="text" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','motto','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.motto}}" bindinput="__e"/></view><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">写给十年后的自己：</text></view><textarea placeholder="60字以内" maxlength="60" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','to_me','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.to_me}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea><view class="flex_item"><text class="label">同学我想对你说：</text></view><textarea placeholder="80字以内" maxlength="80" data-event-opts="{{[['input',[['__set_model',['$0','to_classmate','$event',[]],['data.word']]]]]}}" value="{{data.word.to_classmate}}" bindinput="__e"></textarea></view></view><view class="up_img_title">上传图片<text class="small">/限4张</text></view><view class="image_list"><block wx:for="{{data.images}}" wx:for-item="item" wx:for-index="index" wx:key="index"><view class="item"><image class="cover" src="{{item}}" mode="aspectFill" lazy-load="true"></image><image class="del" data-index="{{index}}" src="../../static/icon_del.png" mode="aspectFit" data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['del',['$event']]]]]}}" bindtap="__e"></image></view></block><block wx:if="{{data.images.length<maxNum}}"><view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['upImage',['$event']]]]]}}" class="item" bindtap="__e"><image class="cover" src="../../static/btn_addimage.png" mode="aspectFill"></image></view></block></view><view class="tips"><text class="color_main">*</text>请按要求填写并上传（文字不能漏填，照片张数不能少，否则 无法为您提供设计服务）</view><cover-view class="btns"><cover-view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['upTemp',['$event']]]]]}}" class="btn color_main" bindtap="__e">自己上传</cover-view><cover-view data-event-opts="{{[['tap',[['start',['$event']]]]]}}" class="btn bg_main" bindtap="__e">开始设计</cover-view></cover-view></view></view>